description: Two Palestinians are arrested after several cars are used in what police say was a terrorist attack.
maintext: Tensions have also been heightened in the West Bank since the start of the war in Gaza. Local health officials say more than 350 Palestinians have been killed by Israeli forces in raids targeting militants and in other incidents, as well as in settler-related violence.
title: Israel: Woman killed, 17 hurt in suspected Palestinian car-ramming attack
